===Estanque de la Luz===
;Description
:You can´t miss the Estanque de la Luz when you go to Parras! It´s the most obvious and fun use of water in the town. It is used as a swimming pool and as a water source for irrigation.

;Location
:6 blocks west and 2 blocks south of UTC. 

;Justification
:The Estanque is AT because it has two uses, for fun, and for irrigation. 

;Issues
:The water that fills the tank comes from the nearby mountains and is a seemingly endless resource. Or is it? When will it run out?  

