==Washtubs==
;Description
:The washtubs on the irrigation canal below Estanque de la Luz are used by the local people for washing clothes. 

;Justification
:The washtubs below the Estanque may or may not be AT depending on what type of soap they use. The good part is that clothes are being washed without using [[electricity]] and are probably being dried by the sun on a line.

;Issues
:If the people are using non-biodegradable soap in the wash tubs, it is polluting the environment. A possible solution would be to try to get the people to start using more environmentally friendly [[soaps]]. One plant that grows nearby can be used as a soap. 

