===Community Irrigation===
;Description
:The water supply for the town is shared publicly through channels that run throughout the town and are directed towards different areas of the town at different times of the day. 

;Location
:The channels are located along the streets of Parras. 

;Justification as [[Appropriate]]
:It is an example of [[appropriate technology]] because it makes directs the water of the town by using gravity rather than generators. It also is shared by the entire community, keeping water a public commodity rather than something one has to pay for. 

;Issues with the Appropriateness
The channels are open, exposing the water to serious pollution. The exact schedule of when the water is diverted in each direction is unknown. The sharing of water may not be equal. 

